title: #218 - Content Court: JayStation
description: On this episode of CONTENT COURT, the Honorable Judge Ethan Klein and Officer Hila take a close look at YouTube legend JayStation's spooky content. You know the legend of JayStation, the man who faked his girlfriend's death for views and subs, but are you aware of the REAL JayStation? Find out more than you ever wanted to know on this edition of Content Court!
